data.description: Three acres in the Heart of Farmington! Home has lots of updates throughout and move-in ready. Set back off the main road, this rambler home offers privacy which is rare to find in Farmington. With four bedrooms, two baths, lots of closet storage, generous living space and quality finishes, wood burning fireplace for cold winters days, you'll enjoy this perfect home for relaxing and enjoying the outdoors. Home offers main-floor living & plenty of natural light flows throughout the home's open, airy layout. The kitchen will inspire your inner culinary skills with its quartz counters, updated cabinets, sink, flooring and stainless appliances. Four car insultaed-heated garage to store your Boat, ATV/UTV, or all your toys. Above the garage is a unfinished loft area for storage or potential to add a private office or rec room.  Screened in porch and pool with deck for hot summer days & bbq's. Shared driveway for extra help with maintenance and snow removal. Home is on slab with no basement.
